    {
      "id": "dict-demotion-note-risk",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Risk",
      "position": {
        "x": 720,
        "y": 660
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Risk\n\nDo not remove the dictionary object faster than the replacement declaration surfaces become real. The danger is not losing the object. The danger is losing explicitness.\n\nThe live residue is now support:\n- cached lookup\n- fallback resolution hints\n- compatibility for old graphs\n- explicit legacy editing surfaces that have not yet been fully retired",
